com.swedbank.sdk.banklink

Interface BanklinkClient


  • public interface BanklinkClient
    Provides methods for interacting with the Swedbank app, such as by generating Intents that initiate banklink transactions.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      android.content.Intent createBanklinkIntent(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> packet)
      Creates an Intent that can be used to initiate a Swedbank banklink transaction.
      boolean isSupportedSwedbankAppInstalled() 
      void openSwedbankAppPlayStoreListing()
      Opens the Swedbank app install page in the Google Play Store according to provided locale.
      BanklinkResult parseResult(int resultCode, android.content.Intent data)
      Parse the result from the Swedbank app for initiated banklink transaction.

    • Method Detail

      • isSupportedSwedbankAppInstalled

        boolean isSupportedSwedbankAppInstalled()
        Returns:
        true if a version of the Swedbank app that supports the Banklink API is installed, false otherwise.

      • createBanklinkIntent

        android.content.Intent createBanklinkIntent(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> packet)
                                     throws android.content.ActivityNotFoundException
        Creates an Intent that can be used to initiate a Swedbank banklink transaction. Provide the created Intent to the Activity.startActivityForResult(Intent, int) to initiate the transaction.
        Parameters:
        packet - packet data.
        Throws:
        android.content.ActivityNotFoundException - if the Swedbank app is not installed.
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if packet is null.

      • openSwedbankAppPlayStoreListing

        void openSwedbankAppPlayStoreListing()
                              throws android.content.ActivityNotFoundException
        Opens the Swedbank app install page in the Google Play Store according to provided locale. The Play Store activity is started using the application context.
        Throws:
        android.content.ActivityNotFoundException - if there is no app that can open Play Store listing.

      • parseResult

        BanklinkResult parseResult(int resultCode,
                           android.content.Intent data)
        Parse the result from the Swedbank app for initiated banklink transaction.

        This method must be called in Activity#onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data).

        Parameters:
        resultCode - result code in the Activity#onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data)
        data - data in the Activity#onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data)
        Returns:
        Parsed transaction result.
